{"story":{"group_1":[{"armatureList":[{"animation":["action"],"armatureId":1,"filePath":"resource/image_native/effect/story/general/3504_picture-story_show_frame.ExportJson","zOrder":"messageBack"}],"autoTurnLast":1,"bg":"black","item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/32502_holy_mami_anime_ver_story/episode21_2.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"setVisible":1,"zOrder":"charaBack"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":1.5,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnChangeOutTime":0.2},{"nameNarration":"Mami","narration":"...And then...","narrationAnchor":"bottom","narrationCoverOpacity":110,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationFontSize":30,"narrationLineMargin":60,"narrationLineSpace":20},{"bg":"white","narration":"Suddenly, I didn't know what I was doing anymore,@and I didn't even understand myself..."},{"bgm":"bgm02_anime17","narration":"I was able to come back to my senses"},{"narration":"thanks to Kaname-san and the others removing the Rumor..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"autoTurnLast":1.2,"flashEffect":"explosion","item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/32502_holy_mami_anime_ver_story/episode21_2.jpg","setVisible":0}]},{"nameNarration":"Mami","narration":"When Kaname-san and Miki-san removed the Rumor@from me to protect me from my current state,","narrationAnchor":"bottom","narrationCoverOpacity":110,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationFontSize":30,"narrationLineMargin":35,"narrationLineSpace":20},{"narration":"memories flooded back into me..."},{"autoTurnLast":1,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/32502_holy_mami_anime_ver_story/episode21_3.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"charaBack"}],"nameNarration":"Mami","narration":"As a Magical Girl, I had always fought alone,","narrationAnchor":"bottom","narrationCoverOpacity":110,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationFontSize":30,"narrationLineMargin":60,"narrationLineSpace":20},{"bg":"black","narration":"so I was very happy when Kaname-san and Miki-san@became Magical Girls and joined me as comrades."},{"narration":"But after coming to Kamihama and learning about@the cruel fate of Magical Girls..."},{"narration":"I realized how horribly I treated them..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"autoTurnLast":0.8,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/32502_holy_mami_anime_ver_story/episode21_3.jpg","visible":"hide"}]},{"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/32502_holy_mami_anime_ver_story/episode21_4.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"charaBack"}],"nameNarration":"Mami","narration":"So I thought that I should forever be alone...","narrationAnchor":"bottom","narrationCoverOpacity":110,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationFontSize":30,"narrationLineMargin":35,"narrationLineSpace":20},{"narration":"Even though I believed I could do anything to@liberate everyone from the fate of Magical Girls..."},{"narration":"Somehow... I ended up being taken in by the Rumor@and losing my sense of self."},{"narration":"I was about to lose the very people I was trying to save..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"autoTurnLast":0.8,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/32502_holy_mami_anime_ver_story/episode21_4.jpg","visible":"hide"}]},{"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/32502_holy_mami_anime_ver_story/episode21_5.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"charaBack"}],"nameNarration":"Mami","narration":"...Of course, Kaname-san and the others had every reason to@despise me, and it'd only be natural for them to hate me...","narrationAnchor":"bottom","narrationCoverOpacity":110,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationFontSize":30,"narrationLineMargin":35,"narrationLineSpace":20},{"narration":"But when I woke up..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"autoTurnLast":0.8,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/32502_holy_mami_anime_ver_story/episode21_5.jpg","visible":"hide"}]},{"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/32502_holy_mami_anime_ver_story/episode21_6.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"charaBack"}],"nameNarration":"Mami","narration":"My dear friends were by my side... They warmly welcomed me...","narrationAnchor":"bottom","narrationCoverOpacity":110,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationFontSize":30,"narrationLineMargin":35,"narrationLineSpace":20},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"autoTurnLast":0.8,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/32502_holy_mami_anime_ver_story/episode21_6.jpg","visible":"hide"}]},{"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/32502_holy_mami_anime_ver_story/episode21_4.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"charaBack"},{"opacity":150,"path":"resource/scenario/img/black.png","posX":0,"posY":0,"scale":2,"setVisible":1,"zOrder":"charaFront"}],"nameNarration":"Mami","narration":"Even though I had been so timid and pitiful@and had always been alone...","narrationAnchor":"bottom","narrationCoverOpacity":110,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationFontSize":30,"narrationLineMargin":35,"narrationLineSpace":20},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/32502_holy_mami_anime_ver_story/episode21_4.jpg","visible":"hide"}]},{"autoTurnLast":0.6,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/black.png","setVisible":0}]},{"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/32502_holy_mami_anime_ver_story/episode21_7.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"charaBack"}],"nameNarration":"Mami","narration":"I...wasn't alone anymore.","narrationAnchor":"bottom","narrationCoverOpacity":110,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationFontSize":30,"narrationLineMargin":35,"narrationLineSpace":20},{"narration":"Kaname-san was there."},{"narration":"Miki-san was there."},{"narration":"And Akemi-san and Sakura-san too...!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.5,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"autoTurnLast":0.8,"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/32502_holy_mami_anime_ver_story/episode21_7.jpg","visible":"hide"}]},{"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/32502_holy_mami_anime_ver_story/episode21_8.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"charaBack"}],"nameNarration":"Mami","narration":"We were all together.@That's why I...","narrationAnchor":"bottom","narrationCoverOpacity":110,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationFontSize":30,"narrationLineMargin":35,"narrationLineSpace":20},{"narration":"I decided to face the fate of Magical Girls with everyone."},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"autoTurnLast":3,"bg":"bg_adv_15061.jpg","bgm":"stop","deleteArmatureList":[1],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeInTime":1.5},{"bgm":"bgm02_anime14","nameNarration":"Mami","narration":"Even in the face of the cold truth about Magical Girls,@thanks to my dear friends, I found hope...","narrationCoverOpacity":150,"narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnChangeOutTime":1.5},{"narration":"And this is the end of the miraculous tale of Mami Tomoe."},{"narration":"...Thank you for listening until the very end."},{"narration":"I would love to hear your thoughts on this story,@but I must return home soon."},{"narration":"If we meet again...@Please share your thoughts with me."},{"narration":"And someday...@I'd be happy to talk about our future."},{"narration":"Well then, see you."},{"autoTurnLast":2,"bgm":"stop","narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeInTime":1.2}]},"version":3}
